---
title: Creamy Mushroom Alfredo with Linguine and Spinach
description: Perfect pasta doesn't take a lot of ingredients, or time! This creamy Alfredo has a secret ingredient: soy sauce! Adding soy sauce to the mushrooms gives this Alfredo an umami kick.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-mushroom-alfredo-7dc94d5c.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/creamy-mushroom-alfredo-625ffdfb20252b621744b9c2-229d3bde.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipes/creamy-mushroom-alfredo-625ffdfb20252b621744b9c2
